低… 我这样一个水平一般的画师对此感到非常紧张，因为 AI 进步的速度比画师转变画风要快十倍，画师的作品也会成为 AI 的养料，让它变得更强。 百年前摄影机取代了人像画师，现代机器取代人工，仅仅两三代人的时间人类尝试了智能驾驶，智能烹饪，AI 绘画，AI 写作，3D 打印。（它们的确有很大缺陷但毕竟还很年轻） AI 与人之间可以相互促进，AI 也可以当成强大的辅助，而我现在担心的是我的成长跟不上 AI 的进步，担心 AI 绘画像 2007 年第一代苹果手机一夜之间被全球消费者追求，最终智能手机遍地开花变成绝对日常的物品…画师会不会也被淘汰呢？对非画师来说技术进步是百利而无一害的事情，对我来说这是个可能丢饭碗的事情（难过）。 我在 AI 绘画方面的认知水平很低，希望懂得的人能给出见解。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-f206bb0dfacea3194a9ee2357dd49d4a_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/548966037"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I8rSU+dj+u/QQEAMaCDg0Mjc2MTIzIPuI+JcGMAM4cUAfcgk1NDg5NjYwMzd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "32_1662339708.88914", "card_id": "Q_470177228", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 849}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "职场中，什么样的人会被领导偏爱？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-925137116e6e5b0a812e05ca293f141e_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/470177228"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8rSU+dj+u/QQEAMaCDY2NzYzMjg0IJHJiocGMAw44yNAIHIJNDcwMTc3MjI4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "33_1662339708.8901484", "card_id": "Q_549733739", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 104}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "孩子最终成为了普通人，如果你是家长，你会怎么样？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-938ec9d8b79eb525147ce8ea40e9f6ad_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color":